                                                                        <div class="comment-author"> <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <a itemprop="url" href="john.php"> <span itemprop="name">John Peter</span> </a> </span><span class="badge-span" style="background-color: #ffbf00">Pundit</span></div> <a href="https://2code.info/demo/themes/Discy/Main/question/how-to-handle-personal-stress-caused-by-utterly-incompetent-and-lazy-co-workers/#comment-35" class="comment-date" itemprop="url"> <span class="discy_hide" itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2018-04-18T21:48:58+00:00">2018-04-18T21:48:58+00:00</span>Added an answer on April 18, 2018 at 9:48 pm </a>
